WEBVTT

00:00:00.920 --> 00:00:02.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>OCTOBER 22ND</b></Default>

00:00:04.879 --> 00:00:07.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

00:00:10.500 --> 00:00:12.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We have gifts for everyone
from Yotsuba-ya!</b></Default>

00:00:12.789 --> 00:00:14.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Thank you!
-Thanks!</b></Default>

00:00:14.710 --> 00:00:17.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[all speaking at once]</b></Default>

00:00:18.420 --> 00:00:20.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

00:00:20.379 --> 00:00:22.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[UZUKI] I wonder
if I'm experiencing</b></Default>

00:00:22.539 --> 00:00:23.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>puberty syndrome right now.</b></Default>

00:00:24.039 --> 00:00:25.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Probably.</b></Default>

00:00:25.329 --> 00:00:26.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then if I get better</b></Default>

00:00:27.039 --> 00:00:28.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't read
the room anymore, huh?</b></Default>

00:00:29.039 --> 00:00:30.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, probably.</b></Default>

00:00:31.170 --> 00:00:32.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You want some, Uzuki?</b></Default>

00:00:32.500 --> 00:00:33.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's mango orange flavor.</b></Default>

00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:36.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sure. Thank you.</b></Default>

00:00:36.380 --> 00:00:38.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They even have
bitter-pellicle-marron</b></Default>

00:00:38.079 --> 00:00:39.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and matcha-banana, too!</b></Default>

00:00:39.380 --> 00:00:40.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ah! No way!</b></Default>

00:00:40.880 --> 00:00:42.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think I want that one, too.</b></Default>

00:00:42.380 --> 00:00:44.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uzuki? What's the matter?</b></Default>

00:00:46.789 --> 00:00:48.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey.</b></Default>

00:00:48.670 --> 00:00:52.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you girls think we can
actually make it to Budokan?</b></Default>

00:00:52.380 --> 00:00:53.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[all gasping]</b></Default>

00:00:55.710 --> 00:00:57.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ opening theme song playing]</b></Default>

00:02:03.540 --> 00:02:09.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}RASCAL DOES NOT DREAM
OF SANTA CLAUS</b></Default>

00:02:27.539 --> 00:02:28.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}#3 IDOL SONG</b></Default>

00:02:29.039 --> 00:02:29.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}Big brother.</b></Default>

00:02:30.000 --> 00:02:32.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}Are you going to the concert
at Odaiba today?</b></Default>

00:02:32.539 --> 00:02:34.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh-huh. As a date with Mai.</b></Default>

00:02:34.669 --> 00:02:36.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're meeting up after this.</b></Default>

00:02:36.250 --> 00:02:37.669 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No fair.</b></Default>

00:02:37.750 --> 00:02:39.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But aren't you going
to the Hakkejima concert</b></Default>

00:02:39.710 --> 00:02:41.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with Kano tomorrow, Kaede?</b></Default>

00:02:41.879 --> 00:02:43.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, yeah, I am.</b></Default>

00:02:43.289 --> 00:02:44.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I still feel jealous.</b></Default>

00:02:45.000 --> 00:02:47.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I guess I should have asked
Toyohama to spot me a ticket</b></Default>

00:02:47.419 --> 00:02:49.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for you as well, then, huh?</b></Default>

00:02:49.210 --> 00:02:50.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, it's okay.</b></Default>

00:02:50.669 --> 00:02:52.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'd feel bad about asking
for myself.</b></Default>

00:02:57.580 --> 00:02:59.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Could Mai be running late?
I don't see her.</b></Default>

00:03:00.379 --> 00:03:01.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's unusual.</b></Default>

00:03:02.039 --> 00:03:04.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wonder what kind of reward
I can get in return.</b></Default>

00:03:05.379 --> 00:03:06.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh--</b></Default>

00:03:06.669 --> 00:03:08.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[MAI] Hop in.
-[grunts]</b></Default>

00:03:08.379 --> 00:03:10.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, hold on. Mai?</b></Default>

00:03:11.919 --> 00:03:13.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[engine revving]</b></Default>

00:03:13.419 --> 00:03:16.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ upbeat pop music]</b></Default>

00:03:23.919 --> 00:03:26.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, uh, hey, Mai?</b></Default>

00:03:26.289 --> 00:03:28.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-What is it?
-What is this?</b></Default>

00:03:28.419 --> 00:03:30.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's a car. Never seen one?</b></Default>

00:03:31.039 --> 00:03:32.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When did you buy this?</b></Default>

00:03:32.629 --> 00:03:34.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Before the summer break.</b></Default>

00:03:34.419 --> 00:03:36.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>With all the shooting
I've done lately</b></Default>

00:03:36.080 --> 00:03:38.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I haven't been home</b></Default>

00:03:38.919 --> 00:03:40.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And your license?</b></Default>

00:03:40.379 --> 00:03:42.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Can't drive a car without one.</b></Default>

00:03:42.789 --> 00:03:44.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When did you even apply
for this?</b></Default>

00:03:44.710 --> 00:03:46.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Last year.</b></Default>

00:03:46.080 --> 00:03:47.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>While filming
for the morning drama</b></Default>

00:03:48.039 --> 00:03:50.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I occasionally commuted
to driving school.</b></Default>

00:03:50.250 --> 00:03:52.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But if you had time
for all this</b></Default>

00:03:52.080 --> 00:03:54.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we could have been going
on dates together.</b></Default>

00:03:54.330 --> 00:03:55.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We could have</b></Default>

00:03:55.460 --> 00:03:58.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but someone was too busy
studying for entrance exams.</b></Default>

00:03:58.629 --> 00:04:00.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Since you weren't paying
attention to me</b></Default>

00:04:00.379 --> 00:04:02.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I went to get a driver's license
to pass my boredom.</b></Default>

00:04:03.000 --> 00:04:04.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

00:04:04.419 --> 00:04:06.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's with
the big dramatic sigh?</b></Default>

00:04:06.330 --> 00:04:07.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Because my plan is ruined.</b></Default>

00:04:08.039 --> 00:04:09.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was saving up
for my part-time job</b></Default>

00:04:09.960 --> 00:04:11.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to go to driving school.</b></Default>

00:04:11.500 --> 00:04:13.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can still go.</b></Default>

00:04:13.379 --> 00:04:15.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, but I wanted to get
a license secretly</b></Default>

00:04:15.629 --> 00:04:18.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and take you on a drive
for a date as a surprise.</b></Default>

00:04:18.540 --> 00:04:20.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Looks like I beat you to it.</b></Default>

00:04:20.209 --> 00:04:22.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And I got to invite you
on a drive for a date.</b></Default>

00:04:23.420 --> 00:04:24.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Speaking of dates</b></Default>

00:04:24.500 --> 00:04:26.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I heard you and Hirokawa went
on a little date of your own.</b></Default>

00:04:27.000 --> 00:04:29.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, we just went
to Misakiguchi</b></Default>

00:04:29.129 --> 00:04:30.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and ate some tuna bowls.</b></Default>

00:04:30.709 --> 00:04:32.209 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And biked through
a daikon field</b></Default>

00:04:32.290 --> 00:04:33.709 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but that's about it.</b></Default>

00:04:33.790 --> 00:04:35.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I see. That sounds like a date.</b></Default>

00:04:36.500 --> 00:04:37.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, I guess.</b></Default>

00:04:45.670 --> 00:04:46.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh...</b></Default>

00:04:46.829 --> 00:04:48.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So that you don't get lost
in the crowd.</b></Default>

00:04:48.879 --> 00:04:50.709 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Good idea.
I don't have a smartphone</b></Default>

00:04:50.790 --> 00:04:52.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so please don't let go of me.</b></Default>

00:04:52.959 --> 00:04:54.459 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Have you been to Odaiba?</b></Default>

00:04:54.540 --> 00:04:56.959 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Never had a reason</b></Default>

00:04:57.040 --> 00:04:58.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But you come here often, right?</b></Default>

00:04:58.959 --> 00:05:01.209 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Once in a while.
Mostly for work, though.</b></Default>

00:05:08.420 --> 00:05:10.709 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crowd cheering]</b></Default>

00:05:10.790 --> 00:05:12.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thank you, everyone!</b></Default>

00:05:12.379 --> 00:05:14.209 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thanks so much!</b></Default>

00:05:15.459 --> 00:05:17.209 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Looks like we made it
just in time.</b></Default>

00:05:21.250 --> 00:05:22.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ Sweet Bullet's
"Museninaccyau"]</b></Default>

00:05:22.379 --> 00:05:25.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[all singing in Japanese]</b></Default>

00:05:29.000 --> 00:05:30.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crowd cheering]</b></Default>

00:05:30.879 --> 00:05:33.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

00:05:40.129 --> 00:05:42.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[singing in Japanese]</b></Default>

00:05:45.750 --> 00:05:47.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

00:05:47.170 --> 00:05:49.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[singing in Japanese]</b></Default>

00:05:55.750 --> 00:05:57.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[all singing]</b></Default>

00:05:57.129 --> 00:05:59.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[singing in Japanese]</b></Default>

00:05:59.420 --> 00:06:00.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[all singing]</b></Default>

00:06:00.920 --> 00:06:04.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[whispered singing]</b></Default>

00:06:07.629 --> 00:06:10.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[singing in Japanese]</b></Default>

00:06:14.670 --> 00:06:16.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hello and good evening</b></Default>

00:06:16.579 --> 00:06:19.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALL] We are Sweet Bullet!</b></Default>

00:06:19.079 --> 00:06:22.209 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Zukki's voice is the only one
that I can't hear.</b></Default>

00:06:22.290 --> 00:06:24.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It sounds like we're already
pressed for time</b></Default>

00:06:24.750 --> 00:06:26.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so these songs will be our last.</b></Default>

00:06:27.500 --> 00:06:30.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ Sweet Bullet's
"Ultrasonic Melody"]</b></Default>

00:06:30.500 --> 00:06:32.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

00:06:38.920 --> 00:06:41.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[barely audible singing]</b></Default>

00:06:46.879 --> 00:06:49.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Mai, earlier, Zukki...</b></Default>

00:06:49.459 --> 00:06:52.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] I noticed.
She likely lost her voice.</b></Default>

00:06:52.790 --> 00:06:54.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've seen it happen before.</b></Default>

00:06:54.920 --> 00:06:56.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>More often than
you would expect.</b></Default>

00:06:57.420 --> 00:06:59.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>People can temporarily lose
their voice</b></Default>

00:06:59.420 --> 00:07:01.959 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>due to a traumatic event
or intense stress.</b></Default>

00:07:02.040 --> 00:07:03.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Come to think of it</b></Default>

00:07:03.209 --> 00:07:05.209 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>when you and Toyohama
swapped bodies</b></Default>

00:07:05.290 --> 00:07:08.209 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she also became ill from all
the pressure it put her under.</b></Default>

00:07:08.290 --> 00:07:10.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Most people don't realize it</b></Default>

00:07:10.629 --> 00:07:13.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but our bodies and feelings
affect each other tremendously.</b></Default>

00:07:14.040 --> 00:07:14.959 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[cellphone chimes]</b></Default>

00:07:16.329 --> 00:07:17.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's from Nodoka.</b></Default>

00:07:17.750 --> 00:07:19.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uzuki's at the hospital.</b></Default>

00:07:20.000 --> 00:07:22.209 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

00:07:29.629 --> 00:07:30.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[both gasp]</b></Default>

00:07:30.920 --> 00:07:33.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>EMERGENCY RECEPTION</b></Default>

00:07:34.079 --> 00:07:36.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Been a while, Sakuta.
-You, too, Mai.</b></Default>

00:07:36.420 --> 00:07:38.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Zukki, you okay?</b></Default>

00:07:39.670 --> 00:07:41.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Hm.
-I'm sorry.</b></Default>

00:07:41.329 --> 00:07:43.459 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uzuki can't really use
her voice right now.</b></Default>

00:07:43.540 --> 00:07:46.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They told her she should get
plenty of rest and take it easy.</b></Default>

00:07:46.709 --> 00:07:49.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-She has been quite busy lately.
-[gasps]</b></Default>

00:07:53.129 --> 00:07:54.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nodoka and the others
are still speaking</b></Default>

00:07:54.879 --> 00:07:56.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with our manager inside.</b></Default>

00:07:57.000 --> 00:08:00.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sorry to jet, but I'm gonna
take Uzuki home for today.</b></Default>

00:08:00.579 --> 00:08:02.459 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Right. Please take care.</b></Default>

00:08:02.540 --> 00:08:05.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ pensive music playing]</b></Default>

00:08:09.500 --> 00:08:11.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[car door closes]
-[engine turns over]</b></Default>

00:08:15.500 --> 00:08:18.209 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, the talks about Uzuki's
solo debut were true</b></Default>

00:08:18.290 --> 00:08:20.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the whole time? Well, were they?</b></Default>

00:08:20.379 --> 00:08:22.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please, just tell us
the truth already.</b></Default>

00:08:22.629 --> 00:08:24.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Manager!</b></Default>

00:08:25.540 --> 00:08:28.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's true that there are talks
about Uzuki's solo debut.</b></Default>

00:08:28.629 --> 00:08:31.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait, does that mean
she's graduating?</b></Default>

00:08:31.629 --> 00:08:33.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Our chief is considering it.</b></Default>

00:08:33.500 --> 00:08:34.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[all groaning]</b></Default>

00:08:34.960 --> 00:08:37.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But Uzuki has declined
the offer once already.</b></Default>

00:08:38.250 --> 00:08:41.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That was right after she filmed
that new commercial</b></Default>

00:08:41.250 --> 00:08:43.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think at the end of August?</b></Default>

00:08:43.330 --> 00:08:45.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was that long ago?</b></Default>

00:08:45.750 --> 00:08:48.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So that's why our chief
shelved the solo debut offer</b></Default>

00:08:48.289 --> 00:08:49.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>at the time.</b></Default>

00:08:49.539 --> 00:08:51.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But seeing how
the public reacted</b></Default>

00:08:51.289 --> 00:08:52.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to that commercial</b></Default>

00:08:52.629 --> 00:08:54.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it was something
they couldn't give up on.</b></Default>

00:08:54.879 --> 00:08:56.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>After it was unveiled</b></Default>

00:08:56.210 --> 00:08:58.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we started receiving offers
from amazing places</b></Default>

00:08:58.710 --> 00:09:00.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>wanting to produce Uzuki.</b></Default>

00:09:00.960 --> 00:09:03.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did you talk
to Uzuki about all that?</b></Default>

00:09:03.539 --> 00:09:04.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We haven't yet.</b></Default>

00:09:04.710 --> 00:09:07.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Our chief said we'll find a time
to discuss it with her again.</b></Default>

00:09:07.919 --> 00:09:10.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, then why has Zukki
been acting</b></Default>

00:09:10.129 --> 00:09:11.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>kind of out of character lately?</b></Default>

00:09:11.960 --> 00:09:14.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'd like to know what
you think the reason is.</b></Default>

00:09:14.379 --> 00:09:16.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Any ideas what she
was so worried about?</b></Default>

00:09:16.830 --> 00:09:18.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[all sigh]</b></Default>

00:09:19.919 --> 00:09:22.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's fine if you don't want
to tell me.</b></Default>

00:09:22.289 --> 00:09:24.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can resolve it on your own.</b></Default>

00:09:26.169 --> 00:09:29.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In any case, we'll head into
the venue tomorrow as planned.</b></Default>

00:09:29.919 --> 00:09:31.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALL] Yes, ma'am.</b></Default>

00:09:31.250 --> 00:09:32.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just be ready for it.</b></Default>

00:09:33.379 --> 00:09:36.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[turn signal clicking]</b></Default>

00:09:36.879 --> 00:09:39.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ pensive music playing]</b></Default>

00:10:05.080 --> 00:10:06.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[NODOKA] Before the concert</b></Default>

00:10:06.669 --> 00:10:08.669 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she asked us
in the dressing room...</b></Default>

00:10:10.539 --> 00:10:12.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uzuki looked right at us.</b></Default>

00:10:13.169 --> 00:10:14.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And she asked</b></Default>

00:10:14.210 --> 00:10:16.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if we thought we could
actually make it to Budokan.</b></Default>

00:10:17.960 --> 00:10:20.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Any other time I'd have said</b></Default>

00:10:20.460 --> 00:10:21.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>or, "Let's do it together."</b></Default>

00:10:23.129 --> 00:10:24.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even when we were depressed</b></Default>

00:10:24.669 --> 00:10:26.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>about a concert
getting canceled</b></Default>

00:10:26.830 --> 00:10:29.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>when we screwed up during work
and lost confidence</b></Default>

00:10:30.039 --> 00:10:32.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>or when we couldn't gain
any new fans.</b></Default>

00:10:32.580 --> 00:10:34.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And the anxiety
would bring us to tears.</b></Default>

00:10:35.960 --> 00:10:38.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Whenever a member was about
to be crushed by insecurity</b></Default>

00:10:38.830 --> 00:10:40.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we cheered each other up
by saying</b></Default>

00:10:40.879 --> 00:10:42.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"Let's all go
to Budokan together."</b></Default>

00:10:42.879 --> 00:10:44.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Like a catchphrase.</b></Default>

00:10:45.629 --> 00:10:47.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's been the plan
this whole time.</b></Default>

00:10:48.879 --> 00:10:51.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Those words would always
come out before.</b></Default>

00:10:51.710 --> 00:10:53.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But today, they didn't.</b></Default>

00:10:54.080 --> 00:10:56.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not even one of us could say it.</b></Default>

00:10:56.379 --> 00:11:00.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When Uzuki asked</b></Default>

00:11:00.419 --> 00:11:01.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Like they weren't true.</b></Default>

00:11:02.629 --> 00:11:04.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And of course we didn't</b></Default>

00:11:04.500 --> 00:11:07.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>because the one who would always
say it before anyone else...</b></Default>

00:11:07.960 --> 00:11:09.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>was Uzuki.</b></Default>

00:11:10.710 --> 00:11:12.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And whenever we felt uncertain</b></Default>

00:11:13.000 --> 00:11:17.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the one who always pulled
us together was just Uzuki.</b></Default>

00:11:17.580 --> 00:11:19.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The truth is, without her there</b></Default>

00:11:19.830 --> 00:11:22.669 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>me and the other members
wouldn't have the courage we do.</b></Default>

00:11:23.330 --> 00:11:25.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When Uzuki
was feeling uncertain</b></Default>

00:11:25.379 --> 00:11:27.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we couldn't do anything for her.</b></Default>

00:11:27.750 --> 00:11:31.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We'd all just selfishly assumed
that Uzuki would be all right.</b></Default>

00:11:33.250 --> 00:11:35.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] What are you going
to do tomorrow?</b></Default>

00:11:35.710 --> 00:11:38.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think we're performing
without Uzuki.</b></Default>

00:11:38.919 --> 00:11:40.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] Can you do it?</b></Default>

00:11:40.129 --> 00:11:42.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Of course. We have to.</b></Default>

00:11:42.830 --> 00:11:43.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh.</b></Default>

00:11:44.330 --> 00:11:47.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, I have work tomorrow</b></Default>

00:11:47.830 --> 00:11:50.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We can't make Uzuki
even more uncertain.</b></Default>

00:11:51.580 --> 00:11:53.669 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This time</b></Default>

00:11:55.580 --> 00:11:56.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}[♪ upbeat music plays on TV]</b></Default>

00:11:57.039 --> 00:11:57.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}OCTOBER 23RD</b></Default>

00:11:57.960 --> 00:12:00.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}[WOMAN] {\i1}The weather in Kanagawa{\i0}
{\i1}today will be unstable.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:12:00.789 --> 00:12:02.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Though sunny</b></Default>

00:12:03.000 --> 00:12:04.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}of a sudden rainstorm.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:12:04.500 --> 00:12:06.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Make sure you don't leave{\i0}
{\i1}your umbrella behind.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:12:06.919 --> 00:12:07.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[phone rings]
-Huh?</b></Default>

00:12:08.629 --> 00:12:11.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}-Oh, big brother?{\i0}
-Kaede?</b></Default>

00:12:11.250 --> 00:12:13.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I thought you and Kano
were having lunch</b></Default>

00:12:13.379 --> 00:12:15.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-before the concert.
{\i1}-We're eating now.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:12:15.710 --> 00:12:17.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Komi is a bit worried, too.</b></Default>

00:12:18.000 --> 00:12:20.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did you hear anything about
it afterwards?</b></Default>

00:12:20.289 --> 00:12:22.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Toyohama didn't say much else.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:12:22.250 --> 00:12:25.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, Uzuki.
I wonder if she's all right.</b></Default>

00:12:25.080 --> 00:12:27.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles softly]
I think she'll be okay.</b></Default>

00:12:27.080 --> 00:12:28.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Are you sure?{\i0}</b></Default>

00:12:28.250 --> 00:12:30.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, we are talking
about Zukki.</b></Default>

00:12:30.169 --> 00:12:33.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[distant indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

00:12:43.830 --> 00:12:47.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

00:12:50.129 --> 00:12:52.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[children laughing]</b></Default>

00:12:53.129 --> 00:12:56.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[kids giggling]</b></Default>

00:12:56.580 --> 00:12:58.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[people screaming in distance]</b></Default>

00:12:58.169 --> 00:13:00.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Now, our next group{\i0}
{\i1}is one that's been soaring{\i0}</b></Default>

00:13:00.500 --> 00:13:03.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}in popularity here recently.{\i0}
{\i1}Sweet Bullet!{\i0}</b></Default>

00:13:03.539 --> 00:13:06.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crowd cheering]</b></Default>

00:13:06.669 --> 00:13:09.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ Sweet Bullet's
"Otomenote" playing]</b></Default>

00:13:09.539 --> 00:13:12.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

00:13:17.830 --> 00:13:20.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

00:13:28.419 --> 00:13:31.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[singing in Japanese]</b></Default>

00:13:33.379 --> 00:13:36.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[singing in Japanese]</b></Default>

00:13:50.000 --> 00:13:52.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[all singing in Japanese]</b></Default>

00:13:55.000 --> 00:13:56.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crowd cheering]</b></Default>

00:13:56.379 --> 00:13:58.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Hello there, everyone!{\i0}</b></Default>

00:13:58.129 --> 00:13:59.669 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thanks for coming today!</b></Default>

00:13:59.750 --> 00:14:02.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALL] And we are Sweet Bullet!</b></Default>

00:14:02.419 --> 00:14:04.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hold on. Aren't we
missing somebody today?</b></Default>

00:14:04.710 --> 00:14:06.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What? You're gonna
bring that up?</b></Default>

00:14:06.419 --> 00:14:07.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, I gotta admit</b></Default>

00:14:07.580 --> 00:14:09.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>singing Zukki's part
is tough for me.</b></Default>

00:14:09.580 --> 00:14:11.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[all laughing]</b></Default>

00:14:11.460 --> 00:14:13.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Anyway, what's up with Zukki?</b></Default>

00:14:13.169 --> 00:14:16.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, the crowd just loosened up.
Let it slide, would ya?</b></Default>

00:14:16.129 --> 00:14:17.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crowd laughing]</b></Default>

00:14:17.629 --> 00:14:19.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Come on, Yae.
Talk some sense into her!</b></Default>

00:14:20.039 --> 00:14:21.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It'll be fine.</b></Default>

00:14:21.879 --> 00:14:24.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uzuki will be back
before you know it.</b></Default>

00:14:24.080 --> 00:14:25.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So let's sing together!</b></Default>

00:14:25.919 --> 00:14:27.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crowd cheering]</b></Default>

00:14:28.500 --> 00:14:31.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ Sweet Bullet's
"Ultrasonic Melody"]</b></Default>

00:14:33.879 --> 00:14:35.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This sure is somethin'.</b></Default>

00:14:35.629 --> 00:14:36.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mm-hmm.</b></Default>

00:14:39.879 --> 00:14:42.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[singing in Japanese]</b></Default>

00:14:44.080 --> 00:14:45.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[lights click off]</b></Default>

00:14:45.129 --> 00:14:47.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[singing continues]</b></Default>

00:14:47.250 --> 00:14:48.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[all gasping]</b></Default>

00:14:50.379 --> 00:14:51.669 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

00:14:53.289 --> 00:14:54.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

00:14:57.710 --> 00:14:58.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groans softly]</b></Default>

00:15:00.250 --> 00:15:01.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Our team is working
to figure out</b></Default>

00:15:01.960 --> 00:15:03.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the cause of this issue</b></Default>

00:15:03.289 --> 00:15:05.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so please be patient
for a short while.</b></Default>

00:15:05.460 --> 00:15:07.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

00:15:10.169 --> 00:15:11.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's get out of here.</b></Default>

00:15:11.710 --> 00:15:12.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're gonna catch a cold.</b></Default>

00:15:13.039 --> 00:15:14.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Good call.</b></Default>

00:15:16.379 --> 00:15:17.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

00:15:17.669 --> 00:15:18.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

00:15:27.169 --> 00:15:28.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Fancy seeing you here.</b></Default>

00:15:28.830 --> 00:15:30.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You come to Sweet Bullet
concerts often?</b></Default>

00:15:30.879 --> 00:15:31.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

00:15:33.960 --> 00:15:36.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Don't worry.
I'm not gonna tell anyone.</b></Default>

00:15:37.210 --> 00:15:39.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So you can go ahead
and talk to me.</b></Default>

00:15:40.830 --> 00:15:43.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Guess you knew I lied.
How'd you find out?</b></Default>

00:15:43.629 --> 00:15:46.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Liars are good at pecking
into other people's lies.</b></Default>

00:15:46.789 --> 00:15:49.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, so you're a lie pecker</b></Default>

00:15:49.210 --> 00:15:51.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You mean like a woodpecker?</b></Default>

00:15:51.080 --> 00:15:53.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}Nuh-uh. That would be
an insult to woodpeckers.</b></Default>

00:15:53.629 --> 00:15:55.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}Well, they're a very kind
family of birds</b></Default>

00:15:55.789 --> 00:15:58.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}-so I'm sure they won't mind.
-[chuckles softly]</b></Default>

00:15:59.039 --> 00:16:01.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[UZUKI] I really did
lose my voice</b></Default>

00:16:01.129 --> 00:16:03.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>during the concert yesterday.</b></Default>

00:16:03.169 --> 00:16:05.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Though you probably
don't believe me.</b></Default>

00:16:05.330 --> 00:16:08.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Nah, I believe you.
I was watching from the crowd.</b></Default>

00:16:09.289 --> 00:16:12.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm always here
for all of our concerts.</b></Default>

00:16:12.379 --> 00:16:14.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Hmm?
-The question you asked</b></Default>

00:16:14.080 --> 00:16:16.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-when you walked up.
-Oh.</b></Default>

00:16:16.580 --> 00:16:19.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ever since Sweet Bullet's
very first live performance</b></Default>

00:16:20.000 --> 00:16:23.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've never missed any.
Not even the smallest shows.</b></Default>

00:16:23.330 --> 00:16:25.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Then were there
any other times</b></Default>

00:16:25.460 --> 00:16:28.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-with trouble of this nature?
-[UZUKI] There were.</b></Default>

00:16:28.580 --> 00:16:30.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The stage wasn't as big
as this one</b></Default>

00:16:30.500 --> 00:16:32.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but that time</b></Default>

00:16:32.830 --> 00:16:35.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So how did they handle
the situation back then?</b></Default>

00:16:35.789 --> 00:16:38.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>One of the girls started
singing without a mic.</b></Default>

00:16:38.169 --> 00:16:40.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-The one in the center.
-Huh?</b></Default>

00:16:48.580 --> 00:16:51.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[singing in Japanese]</b></Default>

00:16:52.539 --> 00:16:55.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crowd clapping in rhythm]</b></Default>

00:16:59.830 --> 00:17:02.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So that girl's not gonna
be on stage after all?</b></Default>

00:17:02.580 --> 00:17:04.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is stupid. Let's head back.</b></Default>

00:17:06.000 --> 00:17:08.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's the reality
we face every day.</b></Default>

00:17:09.130 --> 00:17:11.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>After all this time that
we've been trying so hard</b></Default>

00:17:11.710 --> 00:17:14.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we still can't reach
10</b></Default>

00:17:14.539 --> 00:17:16.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] This certainly packs
quite a punch, though.</b></Default>

00:17:17.039 --> 00:17:18.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[UZUKI] Yeah</b></Default>

00:17:18.920 --> 00:17:21.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] In that case</b></Default>

00:17:21.289 --> 00:17:23.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and go join your friends
up there?</b></Default>

00:17:23.500 --> 00:17:25.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[UZUKI] I'm not qualified
to do that.</b></Default>

00:17:25.829 --> 00:17:28.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The truth is, I'm just like
the people from earlier.</b></Default>

00:17:29.170 --> 00:17:31.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I also have a voice
in the back of my head.</b></Default>

00:17:31.710 --> 00:17:33.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>One that laughs at Nodoka
and the girls</b></Default>

00:17:33.710 --> 00:17:35.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who are trying their hardest</b></Default>

00:17:35.460 --> 00:17:37.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for a dream that'll
never come true.</b></Default>

00:17:38.079 --> 00:17:41.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}Knowing that, I can't stand on
the same stage as them anymore.</b></Default>

00:17:44.079 --> 00:17:46.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA]
Toyohama isn't oblivious</b></Default>

00:17:46.130 --> 00:17:48.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-to all of this, you know.
-[gasps]</b></Default>

00:17:48.420 --> 00:17:51.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She realizes that she's an idol
that hasn't made it big</b></Default>

00:17:51.710 --> 00:17:54.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and she's fully aware that
people are laughing at her.</b></Default>

00:17:54.500 --> 00:17:55.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But she keeps going.</b></Default>

00:17:56.329 --> 00:17:59.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sure the same can be said
for the others, too.</b></Default>

00:17:59.170 --> 00:18:01.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They understand that
the way things are now</b></Default>

00:18:01.420 --> 00:18:03.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>they won't make it to Budokan.</b></Default>

00:18:03.579 --> 00:18:05.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They have a proper view
of reality.</b></Default>

00:18:05.750 --> 00:18:07.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then what's the point?</b></Default>

00:18:07.539 --> 00:18:10.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Really?
You're seriously asking that?</b></Default>

00:18:10.380 --> 00:18:12.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's so simple
that even I can imagine it.</b></Default>

00:18:13.170 --> 00:18:15.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps] I know, but...</b></Default>

00:18:15.920 --> 00:18:17.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What should I do?</b></Default>

00:18:18.079 --> 00:18:20.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[singing in Japanese]</b></Default>

00:18:20.500 --> 00:18:22.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[whimpers]</b></Default>

00:18:22.170 --> 00:18:24.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is when you need
to read the room, Zukki.</b></Default>

00:18:25.579 --> 00:18:28.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALL] ♪ Let me sing my song ♪</b></Default>

00:18:28.670 --> 00:18:31.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ Then tell me your thoughts ♪</b></Default>

00:18:31.420 --> 00:18:34.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ Ah ♪</b></Default>

00:18:34.579 --> 00:18:37.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[all singing in Japanese]</b></Default>

00:18:37.829 --> 00:18:40.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[singing in Japanese]</b></Default>

00:18:40.579 --> 00:18:47.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

00:18:50.539 --> 00:18:51.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[speakers screech]</b></Default>

00:18:51.579 --> 00:18:54.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ song playing over speakers]</b></Default>

00:18:54.710 --> 00:18:57.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

00:18:57.880 --> 00:18:59.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crowd gasping]</b></Default>

00:19:00.210 --> 00:19:01.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

00:19:01.380 --> 00:19:03.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crowd cheering]</b></Default>

00:19:04.079 --> 00:19:05.829 line:90% align:center
