00:19:47.079 --> 00:19:49.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8\i1}So, you guys, I decided{\i0}
{\i1}to accept the offer{\i0}</b></Default>

00:19:49.500 --> 00:19:50.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8\i1}for my solo debut.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:19:50.920 --> 00:19:53.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}However, I won't be graduating{\i0}
{\i1}from Sweet Bullet.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:19:53.670 --> 00:19:55.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}I'll make them both work.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:19:55.250 --> 00:19:57.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Then me and my girls can go{\i0}
{\i1}to Budokan together!{\i0}</b></Default>

00:19:57.829 --> 00:20:00.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So I'm asking all our fans!</b></Default>

00:20:00.420 --> 00:20:02.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yae and Hotaru!</b></Default>

00:20:02.329 --> 00:20:04.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nodoka and Ranko, too!</b></Default>

00:20:04.329 --> 00:20:06.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please turn our Budokan dream
into reality!</b></Default>

00:20:06.960 --> 00:20:08.210 line:90% align:center
