00:20:12.539 --> 00:20:14.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Now, onto the encore!{\i0}</b></Default>

00:20:14.380 --> 00:20:15.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Wait a sec. Encore?{\i0}</b></Default>

00:20:15.750 --> 00:20:17.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}-We're not there yet.{\i0}
{\i1}-What?{\i0}</b></Default>

00:20:17.250 --> 00:20:19.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}They haven't asked us{\i0}
{\i1}for an encore yet?{\i0}</b></Default>

00:20:19.289 --> 00:20:20.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Well, that's okay!{\i0}</b></Default>

00:20:20.579 --> 00:20:22.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Let's just{\i0}
{\i1}do the encore anyway!{\i0}</b></Default>

00:20:23.039 --> 00:20:25.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>YOKOHAMA CITY UNIVERSITY</b></Default>

00:20:25.630 --> 00:20:28.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[yawns, sighs]</b></Default>

00:20:30.039 --> 00:20:31.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm?</b></Default>

00:20:34.380 --> 00:20:36.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, Zukki.
You're going home already?</b></Default>

00:20:36.539 --> 00:20:39.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I just submitted my resignation
to student affairs</b></Default>

00:20:39.170 --> 00:20:40.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so I'm outta here.</b></Default>

00:20:40.170 --> 00:20:41.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm?</b></Default>

00:20:41.500 --> 00:20:43.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's rather sudden</b></Default>

00:20:43.960 --> 00:20:46.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You have no regrets
about college?</b></Default>

00:20:46.289 --> 00:20:49.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Big brother</b></Default>

00:20:49.170 --> 00:20:50.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Hm?
-Why I chose</b></Default>

00:20:50.500 --> 00:20:52.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>statistical science
as my major.</b></Default>

00:20:52.500 --> 00:20:54.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, yeah, I do.</b></Default>

00:20:54.250 --> 00:20:56.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll tell you as my gift
for your afterlife.</b></Default>

00:20:56.920 --> 00:20:59.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think I'd rather it be
a parting gift instead.</b></Default>

00:20:59.630 --> 00:21:02.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I felt that it would
help me understand it a little</b></Default>

00:21:02.210 --> 00:21:03.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if I came here.</b></Default>

00:21:03.460 --> 00:21:04.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Understand what?</b></Default>

00:21:05.000 --> 00:21:07.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}What everyone's really about.</b></Default>

00:21:07.500 --> 00:21:09.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I could figure that out</b></Default>

00:21:09.130 --> 00:21:11.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>then maybe I would have
a better understanding</b></Default>

00:21:11.460 --> 00:21:12.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of Nodoka and the others.</b></Default>

00:21:13.460 --> 00:21:16.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I bet you probably have
a similar reason, don't you?</b></Default>

00:21:16.130 --> 00:21:18.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The reason why you chose
statistical science, I mean.</b></Default>

00:21:19.630 --> 00:21:21.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, I already told you.</b></Default>

00:21:21.420 --> 00:21:24.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I simply chose a major that
gave me the highest chance</b></Default>

00:21:24.170 --> 00:21:26.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-of being accepted.
-Exactly!</b></Default>

00:21:26.250 --> 00:21:28.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's why I'm leaving
all the studying to you.</b></Default>

00:21:28.670 --> 00:21:30.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Once you figure it out</b></Default>

00:21:30.829 --> 00:21:32.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did you even listen
to what I said?</b></Default>

00:21:32.750 --> 00:21:35.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, I ignored
that part intentionally.</b></Default>

00:21:35.210 --> 00:21:37.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[wind blowing]</b></Default>

00:21:39.250 --> 00:21:40.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've gotta get going now.</b></Default>

00:21:41.210 --> 00:21:42.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm!</b></Default>

00:21:42.210 --> 00:21:43.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

00:21:45.670 --> 00:21:47.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Hey, Zukki.
-Hm?</b></Default>

00:21:48.920 --> 00:21:50.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Congrats, new grad.</b></Default>

00:21:50.670 --> 00:21:51.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

00:21:52.539 --> 00:21:53.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles softly]</b></Default>

00:21:54.250 --> 00:21:55.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, see ya!</b></Default>

00:21:56.670 --> 00:21:58.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

00:21:59.250 --> 00:22:01.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

00:22:04.960 --> 00:22:07.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Big brother! Bye-bye!</b></Default>

00:22:08.329 --> 00:22:11.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Bye-bye! Bye-bye!</b></Default>

00:22:11.289 --> 00:22:12.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Bye-bye!</b></Default>

00:22:12.920 --> 00:22:14.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Bye-bye!</b></Default>

00:22:16.829 --> 00:22:18.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Bye-bye!</b></Default>

00:22:21.579 --> 00:22:24.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[wind blowing]</b></Default>

00:22:25.920 --> 00:22:27.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, dear. What a waste.</b></Default>

00:22:27.630 --> 00:22:29.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>After everything I did
to make her able</b></Default>

00:22:29.630 --> 00:22:31.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-to read the room, too.
-[gasps]</b></Default>

00:22:33.460 --> 00:22:34.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles softly]</b></Default>

00:22:35.039 --> 00:22:36.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How surprising!</b></Default>

00:22:36.539 --> 00:22:38.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So you can actually see me!</b></Default>

00:22:38.539 --> 00:22:41.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Guess I gotta hand it to you</b></Default>

00:22:42.630 --> 00:22:44.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And who are you, exactly?</b></Default>

00:22:44.670 --> 00:22:47.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, come on.
You should know that by now.</b></Default>

00:22:47.460 --> 00:22:48.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm?</b></Default>

00:22:49.079 --> 00:22:52.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>'Cause my name
is Touko Kirishima.</b></Default>

00:22:55.579 --> 00:22:57.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ closing theme song playing]</b></Default>

00:22:57.920 --> 00:23:00.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ Uzuki Hirokawa's
"The Horizon is my Scar"]</b></Default>

